categories: Category:Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II actors

nodes.text: Bennet Guillory is the actor who played Jedi Master Qu Rahn in the cutscenes of Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II, credited as "Bennett Gilory" in the game's instruction manual. He also played a Medical Big Shot in Star Trek in an episode of Deep Space Nine and is thus one of the actors to have appeared in both Star Wars and Star Trek material. He also appeared in two episodes of Babylon 5.
